1. Pisac je razradio *scenario* do najsitnijih detalja. (The writer developed the script down to the smallest details.)
2. *Scenario* je bio inspirisan stvarnim događajima. (The script was inspired by real events.)
3. *Scenario* je napisan na engleskom jeziku. (The script is written in English.)
4. Producenti su odbacili *scenario* jer se činio previše kompleksnim. (Producers rejected the script because it seemed too complex.)
5. Uprkos lošim kritikama, *scenario* je postigao veliki uspeh na blagajnama. (Despite bad reviews, the script was a huge success at the box office.)
6. Glumci su uvežbavali *scenario* nedeljama pre snimanja. (Actors rehearsed the script for weeks before filming.)
7. Film ima izvorni *scenario* koji je nagrađen na međunarodnom festivalu. (The film has an original script that was awarded at an international festival.)
8. *Scenario* se fokusira na život mlade umetnice koja se bori sa depresijom. (The script focuses on the life of a young artist who struggles with depression.)
9. Režiser je tražio savršen *scenario* pre nego što je započeo snimanje. (The director was looking for the perfect script before starting filming.)
10. Autor *scenarija* je dobio priliku da režira svoj film. (The scriptwriter got a chance to direct his own movie.)